id: pmc-yzeq
title: Convert test source to typed TypeScript
description: "Move the node:test coverage from a JavaScript .mjs source file to TypeScript, add a dedicated test compiler config, and run tests from compiled output so repository-authored code remains TypeScript-only."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[2]: testing,typescript
created_at: "2026-05-23T22:14:51.489Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-23T22:18:06.603Z"
deadline: "2026-05-24T00:00:00.000Z"
author: codex
estimated_minutes: 45
acceptance_criteria: "- test/generator.test.ts replaces the JavaScript test source.\\n- tsconfig.test.json compiles tests with allowJs=false.\\n- npm test builds source, builds tests, and runs node --test on compiled test output.\\n- dist-test is ignored and never published."
parent: pmc-t7ie
reviewer: steve
risk: medium
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-05-release
release: v2026.05.23-7
resolution: "Converted repository test authoring from JavaScript to TypeScript with compiled node:test execution."
expected_result: "Repository-authored test source is TypeScript, compiles with allowJs disabled, and the Node test suite remains green."
actual_result: "test/generator.test.ts replaces test/generator.test.mjs, tsconfig.test.json compiles tests with allowJs=false into ignored dist-test output, npm test runs node --test dist-test/*.js, and npm run release:check passed with 18 tests."
